cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically video object segmentation, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also utilizes deep learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves experiments and analysis of different convolutional neural networks, which could fall under the sub-categories of cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics).
